Class EntryRequest

java.lang.Object
com.prototype.model.entities.EntryRequest
@Entity public class EntryRequest extends Object
Entity that represents a request to authorize the entry of technological or biomedical equipment into the institution.

This entity records who made the request, which equipment is involved, the stated purpose, the timestamp of creation, and the request type.

Instances of this class are persisted in the entry_request table.
